[Chapter 1: Nightclub Murder Case]

879
00:36:10,150 --> 00:36:10,740
[Police]

880
00:36:11,030 --> 00:36:11,960
Director Zhang,

881
00:36:12,230 --> 00:36:13,590
I have a question.

882
00:36:13,670 --> 00:36:14,530
I'm listening.

883
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:17,280
Director Gao said that when Chief Lu

884
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:19,070
had his accident, you were in Sanjiangkou

885
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:21,130
and personally involved in the case.

886
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:24,700
This matter...

887
00:36:25,450 --> 00:36:26,310
is a long story.

888
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:30,070
Chief Lu had the habit of taking a walk

889
00:36:30,070 --> 00:36:31,400
after dinner every day.

890
00:36:31,840 --> 00:36:33,370
It rained heavily that day.

891
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:35,850
He was in a hurry to get home.

892
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:39,230
I doubt it.

893
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:43,550
I doubt it. I doubt it.

894
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:46,480
I doubt it. I doubt it. I doubt it.

895
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:48,510
Zhang.

896
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:50,760
Last night, I rushed to the scene

897
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:51,870
immediately.

898
00:36:52,150 --> 00:36:53,840
After careful investigation,

899
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:55,670
it was confirmed to be
just a traffic accident.

900
00:36:55,670 --> 00:36:57,110
It couldn't be a criminal case.

901
00:36:57,110 --> 00:36:59,170
There's nothing to be suspicious of.

902
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:01,720
So,

903
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:03,840
it was determined to be an accident.

904
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:10,290
Director Zhang.

905
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:11,940
How are you going to

906
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,130
take the first step?

907
00:37:15,030 --> 00:37:15,440
Right.

908
00:37:16,710 --> 00:37:17,970
Where should we start?

909
00:37:18,670 --> 00:37:20,920
Chief Lu's case
has already been concluded.

910
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:22,030
Going there to investigate

911
00:37:22,030 --> 00:37:23,360
with such great fanfare

912
00:37:23,840 --> 00:37:24,550
will definitely cause dissatisfaction

913
00:37:24,550 --> 00:37:26,410
among the police in Sanjiangkou.

914
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:28,820
How about we intervene mildly first

915
00:37:29,590 --> 00:37:31,520
with routine internal inquiries?

916
00:37:34,630 --> 00:37:37,000
We can't just
go through the motions either,

917
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:39,400
otherwise it'll be hard
to explain to my mentor.

918
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:40,030
Whether or not

919
00:37:40,030 --> 00:37:41,030
we find new clues,

920
00:37:41,710 --> 00:37:42,750
we will conduct

921
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:44,370
targeted investigations.

922
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:49,000
Li Qian.

923
00:37:49,960 --> 00:37:51,400
When Director Gao introduced you to me,

924
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:51,880
he said

925
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:54,000
you are quick-witted and talented.

926
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:55,510
From now on,

927
00:37:55,510 --> 00:37:57,370
share your thoughts with me more.

928
00:38:02,700 --> 00:38:03,630
Director Zhang.

929
00:38:04,550 --> 00:38:05,360
Your arrival in Sanjiangkou

930
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:07,090
will definitely bring clarity

931
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:08,480
to the situation.

932
00:38:10,780 --> 00:38:11,510
Get to the bottom

933
00:38:11,510 --> 00:38:12,710
of this case.

934
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:14,260
I want everyone to know

935
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:16,110
that you, Zhang Yi'ang,

936
00:38:16,110 --> 00:38:17,000
are absolutely not a

937
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:18,590
good-for-nothing loser.

938
00:38:21,670 --> 00:38:22,440
I hope so.

939
00:38:32,930 --> 00:38:38,170
[Warning: High Voltage. No Water Spraying]

940
00:38:44,010 --> 00:38:46,170
♪ This city is called Sanjiangkou ♪

941
