♪ When I first arrived,
no one here shared my vibe ♪

942
00:38:48,590 --> 00:38:51,050
♪ Some people need help
to pull off big plans ♪

943
00:38:51,180 --> 00:38:53,760
♪ Burning their brains
just to chase both fame and fortune ♪

944
00:38:51,730 --> 00:38:53,580
[I hereby report, under my real name]

945
00:38:53,860 --> 00:38:56,100
